{"tid":2237552,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日午餐：牛排配意式鯷魚橄欖醬","createTime":"2020-10-10T11:21:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T10:55:49.000Z","uid":93141,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"542815c121918bc358ea705e596325edecb6a667","tid":2237552,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T11:21:28.000Z","msg":"尋晚同左roommate去飲酒，發生咩事就有機會再講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n起身即刻餓到仆街，煮返個weekend牛排先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UWR5Joa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUWR5Joa.jpg&h=1d917af5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n材料：牛排(我用肉眼)，番茄切塊，鯷魚切碎，橄欖切碎，蒜頭切碎，酸豆切碎，辣椒切碎，香芹切碎，白酒，胡椒，鹽<br />\n<br />\n胡椒，鹽醃牛排，用超大火煎牛排，每面30秒後攞起<br />\n同pan中火炒蒜頭，鯷魚。蒜頭開始變色時落橄欖，酸豆，辣椒<br />\n香味出黎後落白酒，溶走pan面既梅納反應物後落番茄，蓋起焗30秒<br />\n牛排放番茄上，蓋起焗兩分半(medium)，鍾意生d熟d就呢到調整<br />\n攞起牛排，汁內加香芹，煮到想要既濃稠度就搞掂<br />\n<br />\n牛排都係其次，個汁配麵包完全係一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a83011948866679f5c5e324c060ac3294600cbcd","tid":2237552,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T11:21:41.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"5631cfb7cfb0f8bce92edbd50f2b4b0d33e1eaec","tid":2237552,"uid":93141,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T11:21:47.000Z","msg":"Rare image of my roommate幫手煎牛排<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UVQm1ad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUVQm1ad.png&h=86f2ee66&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5af0a1d6bcdb21b4847cf31c4f17b74e5c3ebf94","tid":2237552,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T11:22:04.000Z","msg":"牛扒蕃茄組合好少見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d436dd45c58b945ece6a2e8d7687bbba0374db80","tid":2237552,"uid":93141,"like":0,"disli